library(tidyverse)
library(ipumsr)
alllacounty = data %>%
  filter(COUNTYFIP == 37) %>% 
  group_by(PUMA) %>% 
  summarise(total = sum(PERWT))
  
indianslacounty = data %>% 
  filter(COUNTYFIP == 37) %>% 
  filter(RACED == 610) %>% 
  filter(HISPAN == 0) %>% 
  group_by(PUMA) %>% 
  summarise(indians = sum(PERWT))

calcslacounty = full_join(
  alllacounty,
  indianslacounty
) %>% 
  mutate(indians = replace_na(indians, 0)) %>% 
  mutate(pctindians = indians/total)
Joining, by = "PUMA"
calcslacounty
